 performing is both destructive and civilizing.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aArt and society. 0aPerformance artxPolitical aspects. 0aPerformance artxSocial aspects. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2024z978311074979340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300274752?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300274752423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300274752/original  a978-3-11-074979-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2024b2024  aEBA_EMB  aGBV-deGruyter-alles